Package: TRRident
Type: Package
Title: T Cell Entry Region Identification in Spatial Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Collaborator", "Name", role = "aut")
    )
Description: A computational framework for identifying T cell entry regions 
    (TRR) in spatial transcriptomics data. The method uses Ising models with 
    impurities to detect regions where T cells enter the tumor core. The 
    workflow includes data preparation from 10x Visium data, estimation of 
    Ising model parameters (J1 and J2), change point detection using negative 
    binomial regression with Polya-Gamma augmentation, and Gibbs sampling to 
    calculate posterior probabilities of region membership.
